Description: 
        Flask
        -----
        
        Flask is a microframework for Python based on Werkzeug, Jinja 2 and good
        intentions. And before you ask: It's BSD licensed!
        
        Flask is Fun
        ````````````
        
        ::
        
            from flask import Flask
            app = Flask(__name__)
        
            @app.route("/")
            def hello():
                return "Hello World!"
        
            if __name__ == "__main__":
                app.run()
        
        And Easy to Setup
        `````````````````
        
        ::
        
            $ easy_install Flask
            $ python hello.py
             * Running on http://localhost:5000/
        
        Links
        `````
        
